173
00:10:02,993 --> 00:10:05,082
ROBERT: I'm not sure.

174
00:10:05,213 --> 00:10:06,257
I guess I'll be
going to Chester.

175
00:10:13,090 --> 00:10:16,441
[sighs]

176
00:10:20,097 --> 00:10:21,446
[door opens]

177
00:10:24,536 --> 00:10:25,407
