205
00:12:29,487 --> 00:12:30,837
What?

206
00:12:30,967 --> 00:12:33,100
I didn't want you to
read it in the papers.

207
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:34,449
Well, tell me.

208
00:12:34,579 --> 00:12:36,146
The rumors are true.

209
00:12:36,277 --> 00:12:37,669
They've just released
their own version.

210
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:38,801
And it isn't a beta test.

211
00:12:38,932 --> 00:12:41,586
It's the full deal.

212
00:12:41,717 --> 00:12:43,937
