224
00:13:14,663 --> 00:13:15,707
We know the software works.

225
00:13:15,838 --> 00:13:17,405
Well, in a cruise
missile maybe.

226
00:13:17,535 --> 00:13:19,842
But we're trying to pack
a lot of information

227
00:13:19,973 --> 00:13:22,149
