231
00:13:28,546 --> 00:13:30,331
Six months.

232
00:13:30,461 --> 00:13:31,549
Six months.

233
00:13:31,680 --> 00:13:33,682
ORRIN MERCER: It's
just bad luck.

234
00:13:33,813 --> 00:13:35,118
