242
00:14:04,365 --> 00:14:05,453
Of course.

243
00:14:05,583 --> 00:14:06,323
I'll meet you there.

244
00:14:24,254 --> 00:14:25,299
[clears throat]

245
00:14:25,429 --> 00:14:26,561
