do this, Robert.

246
00:14:26,691 --> 00:14:27,431
Yes I do.

247
00:14:31,435 --> 00:14:32,262
[door slams]

248
00:14:35,178 --> 00:14:35,962
Take all the time you need.

249
00:14:46,624 --> 00:14:49,976
[footsteps]

250
00:15:27,274 --> 00:15:28,623
[sobbing]

251
00:15:40,635 --> 00:15:42,419
Orrin's already made thearrangements for you to take

252
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,030
your brother back to Boston.

253
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:47,685
No, I will bury him here.

254
00:15:51,602 --> 00:15:53,778
Kevin grew up here.

255
00:15:56,520 --> 00:16:04,137
Six generations of
Cannons are buried here.

256
00:16:04,267 --> 00:16:05,790
Kevin would like that.

257
00:16:05,921 --> 00:16:06,704
Yeah.

258
00:16:09,359 --> 00:16:11,927
