262
00:16:20,457 --> 00:16:21,415
The house

263
00:16:21,545 --> 00:16:23,112
I closed up the house.

264
00:16:26,681 --> 00:16:27,464
Well, then open it.

265
00:16:44,090 --> 00:16:44,916
[beep]

266
00:17:03,065 --> 00:17:06,764
