such a great place.

267
00:17:06,895 --> 00:17:08,244
I always liked it.

268
00:17:08,375 --> 00:17:11,291
ROBERT: Well, I always
wanted to get rid of it.

269
00:17:11,421 --> 00:17:14,207
Kevin loved it.

270
00:17:14,337 --> 00:17:15,121
[door closes]

271
